{"tid":923814,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"［Avengers］如果香港樂壇組隊出去比賽，你點揀人","createTime":"2018-12-01T14:41:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-07T08:26:52.000Z","uid":133435,"like":0,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f251c7dfb1c95be7fb89547e602518d50152ce02","tid":923814,"uid":133435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:41:11.000Z","msg":"準則：<br />\n限定5個歌手+1隊組合<br />\n任何香港樂壇健在既歌手，男女不限，但隊內最少要有1男1女<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會揀：<br />\n-歌手-<br />\n1. 陳奕迅<br />\n鐵膽啦，感情同唱功兼備，咩歌都handle到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. Gin Lee<br />\n歌唱比賽經驗豐富，女將選擇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 李克勤<br />\n揀黎唱舊歌，合唱做和音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 郭富城<br />\n揀黎唱快歌同跳舞歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 許廷鏗<br />\n最後一個位會畀佢，叫做有個後生啲而各方面都唔差既在陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n-組合-<br />\n1. Rubberband<br />\n風格夠溫暖，畀到聽眾親切感，拎黎比賽應該打動到評判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2198dc5f2bde9d5c467f82b204a28b42629f0b22","tid":923814,"uid":186711,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-01T14:42:39.000Z","msg":"無張敬軒<br />\n差評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6a6a59171d868a9a61ed8d1a87ad25e97af6c2b","tid":923814,"uid":133435,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2198dc5f2bde9d5c467f82b204a28b42629f0b22","tid":923814,"uid":186711,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,